{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I worked in a company who was the [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really were a steel, steel manufacturers and also anything that goes with steel, you know nails, screws, everything like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And why I mention it is because in those days, when there was no food, it was really nearly a starvation diet, we couldn't afford the black market.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we had to do is go into the countryside and try and find food in, in the villages in-- with the peasants.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I must say, they were horrible to us because they were not so much interested in money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were interested in goods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where should we get goods from?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the, the company was good enough to let us have-- which was difficult to obtain, except because we worked there-- nails or screws or anything like that that you could barter with them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we took it in turn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes it was my turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes it was my father's turn, sometimes my big brother's turn to go to the country and find food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How did you get there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we to-- we had to take a train from Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And although my father was dead against that I should have a bicycle-- but I did get a bicycle because I needed it to go to work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I put a bicycle on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Le Puy, which is in the Haute-Loire, I used to take with my bike-- climb the mountains with a bike-- with a little-- I had a case and a rucksack.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to leave in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it wasn't heated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was freezing cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used to sleep in a little hotel where it was not heated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was not covered properly.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
